{"tid":364917,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[估法官] 陳志雲案律政司上訴得直原審庭需按上訴庭指示判刑","createTime":"2017-08-18T19:30:15.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-18T21:05:50.000Z","uid":127728,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5df882734e57b2f584d58daab71b4cda313c6cca","tid":364917,"uid":127728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T19:30:15.000Z","msg":"2013年<br />\n陳志雲再脫罪律政司照咬唔放<br />\n認為官無正確處理證供　表明上訴<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20130308/18188616\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fart%2F20130308%2F18188616&d=jKMfaIENg%2FsepRZOusneRxxs2jlPaATBKfveiEY0UFo%3D&h=b59fbb4d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fart%2F20130308%2F18188616&h=746450c7\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20130308/18188616</a><br />\n<br />\n2014年<br />\n陳志雲涉貪　原審法官須修改理據 <br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20140826/18844715\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fart%2F20140826%2F18844715&d=jKMfaIENg%2FsepRZOusneRxxs2jlPaATBKfveiEY0UFo%3D&h=811e8151\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fart%2F20140826%2F18844715&h=74cff744\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20140826/18844715</a><br />\n<br />\n2015年<br />\n上訴庭下令原審法官裁定陳志雲罪成 <br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20151026/54354231\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20151026%2F54354231&d=jKMfaIENg%2FsepRZOusneRxxs2jlPaATBKfveiEY0UFo%3D&h=4777a1d2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20151026%2F54354231&h=82d50bbf\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20151026/54354231</a><br />\n<br />\n2015年<br />\n陳志雲申暫緩定罪<br />\n上訴庭：本末倒置<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20151216/19414066\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fart%2F20151216%2F19414066&d=jKMfaIENg%2FsepRZOusneRxxs2jlPaATBKfveiEY0UFo%3D&h=53579b08\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fart%2F20151216%2F19414066&h=bae92053\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20151216/19414066</a><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>上訴庭副庭長楊振權</strong></span>於判詞中指出，上訴庭其實可以直接將陳志雲定罪及判刑，而事實上於今年10月26日上訴庭將案件發還原審法官並下令他改判陳有罪，已等同將陳定罪。<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>上訴庭只為符合人權法規定，才將案件交還原審法官處理，以免剝奪陳向上級法院申請覆核的權利。</strong></span><br />\n上訴庭指被告可依照刑事案件法庭恒常採納的方法提出上訴，但陳的一方指終審庭可能批准陳的上訴許可及最終裁定他上訴得直，並以此作基礎支持原審法官毋須即時定罪的說法，則根本是本末倒置。<br />\n<br />\n2016年<br />\n志雲申請上訴至終審法院被拒 <br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20160126/54689866\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20160126%2F54689866&d=jKMfaIENg%2FsepRZOusneRxxs2jlPaATBKfveiEY0UFo%3D&h=4ea28376\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20160126%2F54689866&h=8235bfb3\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20160126/54689866</a><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>上訴庭今在判詞中指，兩人的理據早已處理，而且不涉重大的廣泛重要性，故不批准兩人上訴至終院。</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n秘撈案　陳志雲准終極上訴<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20160630/19675825\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fart%2F20160630%2F19675825&d=jKMfaIENg%2FsepRZOusneRxxs2jlPaATBKfveiEY0UFo%3D&h=62b97b99\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fart%2F20160630%2F19675825&h=c96435a3\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20160630/19675825</a><br />\n<br />\n2017年<br />\n終院法官：陳志雲案非常奇怪 <br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20170222/19936393\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fart%2F20170222%2F19936393&d=jKMfaIENg%2FsepRZOusneRxxs2jlPaATBKfveiEY0UFo%3D&h=7c11ecfd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fart%2F20170222%2F19936393&h=6b8a8a06\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20170222/19936393</a><br />\n無綫電視前業務總經理陳志雲及其前經理人叢培崑，遭廉署起訴串謀使代理人收受利益，原獲判無罪；律政司兩度上訴，最終上訴庭下令改判有罪，兩人被罰款。<br />\n<br />\n糾纏7年料花過千萬　<br />\n陳志雲終極勝訴　律政司須付訟費<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20170520/20027234\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fart%2F20170520%2F20027234&d=jKMfaIENg%2FsepRZOusneRxxs2jlPaATBKfveiEY0UFo%3D&h=dd933c92\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fart%2F20170520%2F20027234&h=2f653350\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20170520/20027234</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7288a365a3e1bd58759bf253588de3a263343f3","tid":364917,"uid":38795,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T19:32:22.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">楊</span></span>"},{"pid":"9def89a247ddba0af9399e11752e0613143e83c7","tid":364917,"uid":47674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T19:32:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"501a0583c747b855b7616156296891deab653052","tid":364917,"uid":47674,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T19:33:26.00